'''加勒比区域航空883號班機'''是一經[[古巴聖地亞哥|古巴聖地亞哥]]，自[[海地|海地]][[太子港|太子港]]飛往[[古巴|古巴]][[哈瓦那|哈瓦那]]的國際定期航線。2010年11月4日，該班機以[[ATR_72|ATR 72]]執行航班時，在[[聖斯皮里圖斯省|聖斯皮里圖斯省]]墜毀，61位乘客和7名機組人員全數罹難。這次空難為涉及ATR 72的空難中，死亡人數最多的一次，同時也是古巴境內死亡人數第三多的空難。

== 墜機過程 ==
該班機由[[海地|海地]]的[[太子港|太子港]]起飛。<ref name="BBC11700625">{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-latin-america-11700265|title=Passenger plane crashes in Cuba|date=2010-11-05|publisher=BBC News|accessdate=2010-11-05|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101105044410/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-latin-america-11700265|archivedate=2010-11-05}}</ref>航班在16:50離開（[[UTC-4|當地時間]]），自聖地亞哥飛往哈瓦那（[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]20時50分）。<ref name="NYT">{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/reuters/2010/11/04/world/americas/international-uk-cuba-plane.html?hp|title=Plane With 68 Said to Crash in Cuba|work=The New York Times|accessdate=2010-11-05}}</ref>該航班亦是在[[安東尼奧·马塞奥机场|安東尼奧·马塞奥机场]]因[[飓风托马斯|飓风托马斯]]而關閉前的最後一個航班。<ref name="AH4330efa3">{{cite web|url=http://avherald.com/h?article=4330efa3&opt=0|title=Crash: Aerocaribbean AT72 near Guasimal on Nov 4th 2010, impacted ground after emergency call|accessdate=2010-11-05|last=Hradecky|first=Simon|work=The Aviation Herald|archive-date=2016-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160201025414/http://avherald.com/h?article=4330efa3&opt=0|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 大約17:42分時，在飛機發出緊急訊號之後，飛機墜毀於[[圣斯皮里图斯省|圣斯皮里图斯省]]的Guasimal的一個小鎮，大約是在距離哈瓦那{{Convert|210|miles|km|-1}}的位置。<ref name="NYT">{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/reuters/2010/11/04/world/americas/international-uk-cuba-plane.html?hp|title=Plane With 68 Said to Crash in Cuba|work=The New York Times|accessdate=2010-11-05}}</ref>在聽到爆炸聲之前，目擊者指出飛機開的非常的低而且不穩定，並且還冒煙起火。<ref name="Reuters">{{Cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSTRE6A40A320101105|title=Plane with 68 said to have crashed in Cuba|date=2010-11-05|accessdate=2010-11-05|deadurl=no|agency=Reuters|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101108063948/http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSTRE6A40A320101105|archivedate=2010-11-08}}</ref>

空難後，醫療機關很快地進入警戒狀態。但不幸的是，他們在當地時間的午夜時分宣布該航班沒有任何生還者。<ref name="Reuters">{{Cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSTRE6A40A320101105|title=Plane with 68 said to have crashed in Cuba|date=2010-11-05|accessdate=2010-11-05|deadurl=no|agency=Reuters|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101108063948/http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSTRE6A40A320101105|archivedate=2010-11-08}}</ref>

這次空難是涉及[[ATR_72|ATR 72]]中，死亡人數最多的一次。同時也是古巴繼1989年9月3日的[[古巴航空9646號班機空難|古巴航空9646號班機空難]] （171死）和1977年5月27日的[[蘇聯民航331號班機空難|蘇聯民航331號班機空難]]（69死）後，死亡人數第三多的空難。<ref name="ASN041110">{{Cite web|url=http://aviation-safety.net/database/record.php?id=20101104-0|title=Accident description|accessdate=2010-11-05|publisher=Aviation Safety Network|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101108073633/http://aviation-safety.net/database/record.php?id=20101104-0|archivedate=2010-11-08|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="ASN030989">{{Cite web|url=http://aviation-safety.net/database/record.php?id=19890903-1|title=Accident description|accessdate=2010-11-05|work=The Aviation Herald|archive-date=2013-10-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131005095616/http://aviation-safety.net/database/record.php?id=19890903-1|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="ASN270577">{{Cite web|url=http://aviation-safety.net/database/record.php?id=19770527-0|title=Accident description|accessdate=2010-11-05|publisher=Aviation Safety Network|archive-date=2013-04-10|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6FlKPIZkn?url=http://aviation-safety.net/database/record.php?id=19770527-0|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 空難調查 ==
為了進入空難場地，救難人員不得不使用推土機以推開厚厚的植被。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.thesundaily.com/article.cfm?id=53698|title=Rescuers pulling bodies from Cuba plane crash|work=The Sun Daily|accessdate=2010-11-08}}{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>該班機因為撞擊而爆炸，導致機身整個被炸毀。同時，傷者的屍體也被燒得焦黑。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.montrealgazette.com/business/Rescuers+find+black+crashed+Cuban+plane/3780082/story.html|title=Rescuers find black box of crashed Cuban plane|work=The Gazette|accessdate=2010-11-08|deadurl=yes|location=Montreal|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101109005751/http://www.montrealgazette.com/business/Rescuers+find+black+crashed+Cuban+plane/3780082/story.html|archivedate=2010-11-09}}</ref>墜毀時，傷者都還在座位上，這同時也幫助調查人員識別身分。他們也相信他們是因沒有時間反應，導致無法離座。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.google.com/hostednews/ap/article/ALeqM5j4Wxl2-SIsC6W1z3CK8ZjJUPZrCg?docId=de510d217c41487fa16eabc56cab94e8|title=Rescue workers remove bodies from Cuba plane crash|accessdate=2010-11-08|deadurl=no|agency=Associated Press|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101109035346/https://www.google.com/hostednews/ap/article/ALeqM5j4Wxl2-SIsC6W1z3CK8ZjJUPZrCg?docId=de510d217c41487fa16eabc56cab94e8|archivedate=2010-11-09}}</ref>殘骸在墜毀4小時後，火才撲熄。<ref name="NYT_1106">{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2010/11/06/world/americas/06cuba.html?ref=world|title=Cuban Plane Crash Kills 68 People|last=Malkin|first=Elisabeth|date=2010-11-05|work=The New York Times|accessdate=2010-11-06|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110430045627/http://www.nytimes.com/2010/11/06/world/americas/06cuba.html?ref=world|archivedate=2011-04-30}}</ref>遺體隨後被送至[[古巴|古巴]]的法學醫學研究所識別。<ref name="Reuters">{{Cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSTRE6A40A320101105|title=Plane with 68 said to have crashed in Cuba|date=2010-11-05|accessdate=2010-11-05|deadurl=no|agency=Reuters|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101108063948/http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSTRE6A40A320101105|archivedate=2010-11-08}}</ref>

空難發生翌日（11月5日）救難人員找出了[[飛行紀錄儀|飛行紀錄儀]]和駕駛艙錄音器。這些機器隨後被交給調查人員以檢驗和分析。<ref name="Reuters">{{Cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSTRE6A40A320101105|title=Plane with 68 said to have crashed in Cuba|date=2010-11-05|accessdate=2010-11-05|deadurl=no|agency=Reuters|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101108063948/http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSTRE6A40A320101105|archivedate=2010-11-08}}</ref>

11月16日调查当局公布最终结论：极端天气导致飞机机身结冰，机长的不适当操作，最终导致飞机失控。

